  <!-- Engine-managed Odd Jobs role (invisible modded work types) -->
  <WR_OddJobsRole>Odd Jobs</WR_OddJobsRole>
  <WR_ManagedEntriesNote>This role collects jobs that mods add without a Work tab presence. WorkRoles manages its contents automatically: new hidden jobs appear here, and jobs vanish when their mod is removed. You can rename, recolor, reorder, assign and toggle it like any other role — only its job list is off-limits.</WR_ManagedEntriesNote>
  <WR_CannotDeleteManaged>Odd Jobs cannot be deleted: it is where hidden modded jobs are collected. Unassign or disable it instead.</WR_CannotDeleteManaged>

